ties 我淨係記得葉露姍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:39:29.000Z","msg":"佢真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BFNYE9p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBFNYE9p.jpg&h=64f16540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/993wZ9q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F993wZ9q.jpg&h=2822ba69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZVZoRf6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZVZoRf6.jpg&h=cdb76940&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇近況睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dcf732bdfeb562ccd004ab8ce450764a0da9bf4","tid":2084834,"uid":28432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917ebde73a0015601886599c416613ce768c771f","tid":2084834,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:56:16.000Z","msg":"佢政治背景咪社民連同毓民助理🤷🏼🤷🏼🤷🏼"},{"pid":"e2646e04eb01203a573d2addeae5c972b72375f2","tid":2084834,"uid":46587,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"917ebde73a0015601886599c416613ce768c771f","tid":2084834,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:56:16.000Z","msg":"佢政治背景咪社民連同毓民助理🤷🏼🤷🏼🤷🏼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:59:11.000Z","msg":"from wiki<br />\n他自14歲起開始投身社會運動。2009年，受黃毓民影響而加入社民連，<br />\n曾參與反高鐵示威及五區公投。2011年，他跟隨黃毓民退出社民連，同年成為普羅政治學苑第一屆畢業生。2012年，他為第一屆香港中學文憑考試考生，入讀香港大學，後成為黃毓民立法會議員助理[2]，負責政策研究，也曾協助處理司法覆核案件。同年，他參與反國教科活動。<br />\n<br />\n有冇資格做轉世靈童<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cbc29f834ee755110e6ab4ceffb2ce1b1d43438","tid":2084834,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:12:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a